title: Badlands Music Pack 1
description: A hybrid of western, industrial and electronica-styled seamless looping music perfect for a post apocalyptic/futuristic wasteland.
longDescription:
Badlands Music Pack 1 contains a hybrid of western, industrial and electronica-styled music, included are ambient tracks perfect for driving around in a post apocalyptic wasteland and tension tracks designed for combating hordes of mutants. The main tracks are broken down into sub loops to give the user a broader spectrum of music.

All tracks minus fade versions are seamless looping wave files at 44,100 Hz, 16 Bit, Stereo.

Number of Audio Tracks: 37

Intended Platform – All


All my music/audio products are YouTube content ID Free, this means you should never receive a copyright claim from another channel when posting videos to YouTube that include my music. If any issues ever arise please reach out to michael@mlamanna.com.
